Package app.ini.custom.loaders.fsm

Class LineLoader

java.lang.Object
app.ini.custom.loaders.fsm.LineLoader
All Implemented Interfaces:
ILoader 
public class LineLoader
extends java.lang.Object
implements ILoader
For the detailed description of configuration file see: ILoader

This is the concrete implementation of the above ILoader interface. This is an one-file implementation. Using as straight forward approach as possible.

If-else statement is used to determine how the input line should be processed.

The state is spread across all methods.
